{"tid":719593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上連登真係開心過高登好多","createTime":"2018-06-27T14:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T10:47:40.000Z","uid":35870,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52a5bc7e41e41026f2450a75d6c4bd89b329868b","tid":719593,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 連登仔<br />\n<br />\n幾個月前，當公民黨提出要立空置稅<br />\n連登仔: 政府邊會立？政府邊會想樓價跌？個個高官拎住幾廿層樓既得利益者，有用嘅野政府邊會做？<br />\n<br />\n近一兩個月，當有報紙吹風話政府研究緊空置稅<br />\n連登仔: 研究到2046 d官放晒都未落實到啦！政府邊會想樓價跌？<br />\n<br />\n再近一兩個星期，空置稅好似真係會落實<br />\n連登仔: 有撚用咩一手空置稅，係就搞埋二手空置稅啦！唉，不過政府個個幾廿層樓，邊想樓價跌？<br />\n<br />\n今日，好似話林鄭準備開行會出招整個一手空置稅<br />\n連登仔: 出埋d廢招，樓價繼續升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟係連登仔心目中，空置稅有無用架呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊陣時高登就係畀唔到呢d樂趣人，望到連登仔任擺龍門，真係打從心底入面笑出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb888c15d7f87e7cc6a18a61d05fa20da717bf76","tid":719593,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ffddb8479b58d7ad1f9e19e9c8075b69f0c0b0","tid":719593,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa